    // ...

    return filteredData;
}
-----------------------------------------------------

In this snippet, the "Architectural Note" clarifies the reasoning behind the implementation, which helps new team members quickly understand the historical context and performance considerations. It acts as a guide for future modifications, ensuring that key aspects of the design aren’t inadvertently lost during refactoring. This meticulous approach to documentation makes the project more resilient to change over time.
